query:
SELECT 
  tv.messageId, 
  tv.upvotes, 
  tv.downvotes, 
  tv.approved, 
  tv.processedAt as vote_processed_at,
  t.team1,
  t.team2,
  t.status,
  t.processedAt as trade_processed_at,
  t.approvedBy,
  t.team1Players,
  t.team2Players
FROM trade_votes tv
LEFT JOIN trades t ON tv.messageId = t.messageId
WHERE tv.messageId = '1450771119580647539'
